ers of the Native Authority were made to testify before the commission with D.J.M Muffet as sole commissioner. May 18, 2019 In "News" Adam Lamido Sanusi (Ashraf) the son of the Emir of Kano Muhammadu Sanusi II has prayed that between the governor of Kano and the Emir whoever is right should succeed. May 11, 2019 In "News" This piece, first published on June 26, 2014, is reproduced following the dethronement of Alhaji Sanusi Lamido Sanusi as Emir of Kano By ERIC TENIOLA Alhaji Isa Kaita (1912-1994) was the Northern Region Minister for Works between 1954-1957 and later Minister of Education between 1957 and 1966. He later became… March 9, 2020 In "Viewpoint"